    {
      "Name": "Goth Kweebec",
      "Line": "I... Thanks?"
    },
    {
      "Name": "Narrator",
      "Line": "Uh, oh. Other than a stutter, she hardly reacts to your confession."
    },
    {
      "Name": "Goth Kweebec",
      "Line": "Look. I know how this goes."
    },
    {
      "Name": "Goth Kweebec",
      "Line": "I'm flattered, but I'm not going to be that 'weirdo girlfriend' you can show off to your friends."
    },
    {
      "Name": "Goth Kweebec",
      "Line": "Or the 'crazy chick' you're going to gossip about for seasons to come."
    }
  ],
  "AdvanceText": "Continue",
  "End": {
    "Type": "Standard",
    "Line": {
      "Id": "Standard",
      "Text": "If that was your plan, feel free to stop wasting your breath. It's not going to happen."
    },
